                <strong class="text-ink">Supplemental terms:</strong> In certain cases, additional terms or guidelines may apply to specific features or activities. For example, if we run a specific program, event, or contest, there might be separate guidelines or agreements. Any supplemental terms will be disclosed to you in connection with the relevant Service and are hereby incorporated into these Terms by reference. In the event of a conflict between these Terms and any supplemental terms, the supplemental terms will prevail for the specific service they apply to.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="border-t border-ink-divider pt-10 mt-10" id="eligibility">
              <h2 class="ts-heading text-ink mb-4">2. Eligibility</h2>
              <p class="ts-body text-ink-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
                The Services are offered and available only to users who are at least <strong class="text-ink">13 years of age</strong>. By using the Services, you represent and warrant that you are <strong class="text-ink">13 or older</strong>. <strong class="text-ink">If you are under 13 years old, you are not permitted to use our Services.</strong>
              </p>
              <p class="ts-body text-ink-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">
